subs.text: I watched a little MSNBC last night and don't like the way it's going. They're turning the crisis in DC into a horse race.
It's the United States of America vs a gang of thugs.
Don't make the Dem leadership responsible, we all did this.

It's time for the US to grow up. We've had it very very very easy. We fought two wars with no discomfort at home. We are fat and spoiled. This is not the Democrat's problem it's all our problem. Including asshole moderators on TV and Republicans.
